.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
Nationality: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
Flower: iris, tulip, sunflower, daisy, marigold
Beverage: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
Pet: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. Nationality:english == Color:red
2. Nationality:spanish == Pet:dog
3. Beverage:coffee == Color:green
4. Nationality:ukranian == Beverage:tea
5. Color:green is to the right of Color:ivory
6. Flower:iris == Pet:snails
7. Flower:tulip == Color:yellow
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Flower:sunflower is on the left or right of Pet:fox
11. Flower:tulip is to the left or right of Pet:horse
12. Flower:daisy == Beverage:orange-juice
13. Nationality:japanese == Flower:marigold
14. Nationality:norwegian is to the left or right of Color:blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    ukranian	|     english	|    spanish	|    japanese	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Flower		|     tulip	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| daisy	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
